Model:Constraint.name: NamesMustNotBeUsedTwice
Model:Constraint.expression:
context NamedElement
inv: container->isEmpty or (container.oclIsKindOf(Namespace) implies container.contents->forAll(e| e.oclAsType(NamedElement).name = self.name implies e = self))

Model:Constraint.name: InterfaceUseability
Model:Constraint.expression:
context Media
inv: items->forAll(item| (self.sink.isPositive implies self.sink.type.oclAsType(InterfaceType).receive->includes(item)) or ((not self.sink.isPositive) implies self.sink.type.oclAsType(InterfaceType).send->includes(item)))

Model:Constraint.name: TypeSafety
Model:Constraint.expression:
context ArgumentedElement
inv: not type.oclIsKindOf(SignaturedElement) or ( operands->size = type.oclAsType(SignaturedElement).parameters->size and (Sequence { 1 .. operands->size }->forAll(i | self.operands->at(i).determineType() = self.type.oclAsType(SignaturedElement).parameters->at(i).type) or operands->size = 0))
